Title: 147: How to Live a More Fulfilling Life - Time & Energy Management
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with independent turnaround consultant, Vitaly Dolgov. You'll hear about a scheduling system that gets so many things done, know how to block out your time in your calendar and then commit to it, and learn the power of routines by removing unnecessary decision-making.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/147
